values: okay.. this sux summer is half way over and i still have done....<FONT color=#ff0000>NOTHING...lol</FONT><FONT color=#33ff33>..... i am so0o0o bored, i have done nothing this summer i wanted to get a job, but i havent i looked but i have not found... i have nothing to do ever...i <FONT color=#ff0000>NEED</FONT> a life lol  </FONT><FONT color=#ffff00>.... ok u kno the summer is almost over when u get skool supplies...this morning my mom went and got folders binders and all that stuff cuz it was all like 50 cents or a dollar and last year when we went skool shopping we waited till september and by then everything was sold so we learned our lesson </FONT><FONT color=#ff0000>anywayz i was madd this morning...i realllly wanted to go shopping with my mom even though it was nly for skool stuff because i RARELY ever go to the store and when i do its NEVER for me so i wanted to go....but nooooo i had to watch my brother i was like y cant we bring him with us hes got a 20 dollar walmart card lets the kid spend his money and shes all noooooo grrr life bites.....i got over it when she got home lol my anger did not last as long as i wanted it to....</FONT><FONT color=#33ccff>i was thinkin maybe i should write a book lol i day dream alllll day i should put them together and write a book lol i never will though i've tried but i try to hide it cuz i dont want anyone reading it haha....no privacy in this house haha.....</FONT><FONT color=#ffff00>welll im outta stuff to say fer now....buh bye</FONT>

Hello!  i havent wrote in this in a couple dayss... what to say what to say.....my mom is gonna let me get a kitten!!! she said when she has extra money...cuz this week she had to pay her truck bill....and when we find a free kitten we can go and get everything :) ...the only bad part is i have to put the litter box in the basement :( i hate the basement our basement is the crappiest dirties grossiest basement....lol.....i have to clean the liter box every day and all that good stuff....but i finally am gonna get a kitten :)....if we get a boy im gonna name him max :) and i dont kno what ill name it if its a girl....maybe shadow er sumtin....we'll see...well im outta stuff to say laterzzz

  My day....i did nothin today..nothin at allll...my mom didnt go to work till 10 and denny had places to go so i was home alone (which was nice and quiet) and had nothing to do....and nothin on TV...so im bored! haha...i've been searching the net lookin up stupid stuff like penpals and how to draw cartoons and learn a new language on the net....i wanna learn dutch and chinese lol...

ya kno...i tried to talk to u again fer the past two days and u never answer me...and i didnt think u read them cuz when i asked u to read that one u said it was too long...and most of them r so thats y....and just out of curiousity...r we gonna talk thro this from now on or will u talk to me on AIM? i said fuck u cuz u take shit seriously and expect me not to and i wasnt lauging at the fact u ran out of sand so there! lol and i have nothing more to say....

im hot its tooo hot outside...we need air conditioning! but my mom dont wanna bring it upstairs its too heavy...i say i dont wanna go near it cuz thats where all the snakes hung out lol....
u kno i dont kno y i even have this dumb journal thing...i only made it cuz some1 asked me to and they dont even read it themselves! i dont kno i just dont kno...
ppl r so confusing...they joke around all the time and expect u not to take things serious...but when u joke around a bit they freak out and take everything serious...so stupiddd...oh well...life goes on.......

ya know its surprising about how quick ppl get over things...i was pissed yesterday about the job thing...and now im like fuck them who gives a shit...lol...i guess thats a good thing tooooo.
..today was a workin day....i was pooooped out...first we went to some dudes house and got a blade and the york (funny name) then we brought it back and then we filled in half the big hole in our front yard...a thingy umm back hoe i think its called...dug a hole from the street to our house to put in a new water line adn he left it for us to fill in....denny used the tractor...i used a shovel and killed myself lol...well that was my day...

well today i got my phone call....i didnt get the job that i had my interview for.  it sux cuz the dude said the only reason i didnt get hired is because on ONE statement i made i said "i guess" at the end and sounded unsure....i felt like saying FUCK YOU....but i found out the other kid who got the job...his mom works there and is a boss and he did worse on the interview than i did....i hate this world i really do...............
